WEBVTT

00:02.212 --> 00:04.389
This programme
contains some scenes...

00:04.434 --> 00:06.839
which some viewers
may find upsetting.

00:06.884 --> 00:08.845
The ABC railway guide was
beside both dead women.

00:08.890 --> 00:10.935
It is the killer telling
us the rules of the game.

00:10.980 --> 00:12.535
Mr Cust, is there something
you want?

00:12.580 --> 00:13.943
The success of my enterprise.

00:13.988 --> 00:16.076
Would you mind if I joined you,
Sir Carmichael?

00:16.120 --> 00:18.236
Not at all,
but it is quite wild out there.

00:18.281 --> 00:19.831
Whore!

00:19.876 --> 00:23.095
Have I caused you some offence?
You're not who you say you are.

00:23.140 --> 00:31.140
Who the hell are you?

